request.prompt: give me a summary of health and wellness news during August 2025

response.text: I'm unable to provide real-time news updates from August 2025 as I can only access information up to October 2023, and I cannot predict future events. For the most accurate and current health and wellness news from that period, I recommend checking reputable news websites or health-focused publications. These sources typically have sections dedicated to health news and can provide detailed and up-to-date information.
